<div>
    <div id="contact" class="contact scrollspy">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col s12 l6">
                <h4>About Us</h4>
                <p id="aboutUs">
                    Victory Granite and Tiles is recognised as synonymous with quality, and is also said to symbolise the housing of the best style of furniture for interior decoration. At VGT we donâ€™t just sell tiles and furniture, we help transform homes into dreams come true. We excel in room makeovers from start to finish, offering everything from the greatest looks in tiling to amazing furniture for every room and the best selection of accessories around. We are committed to customer satisfaction.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col s12 l6">
                <h4 class="center">Need Our Product? Contact Us!</h4>
                <form name="messageForm">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col s12 input-field">
                            <i class="mdi mdi-alphabetical prefix"></i>
                            <input type="text" name="customerName" id="customerName" class="validate">
                            <label for="customerName">Name</label>
                            <span class="helper-text" data-error="Please provide your name" data-success="Okay"></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col s12 l6 input-field">
                            <i class="mdi mdi-email-outline prefix"></i>
                            <input type="email" name="email" id="email">
                            <label for="email">Email</label>
                            <span class="helper-text" data-error="Invalid Email" data-success="Okay"><em>Email is Optional</em></span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col s12 l6 input-field">
                            <i class="mdi mdi-phone prefix"></i>
                            <input type="text" name="phone" id="phone" class="validate">
                            <label for="phone">Phone</label>
                            <span class="helper-text" data-error="Please provide a valid phone number" data-success="Okay"></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col s12 input-field">
                            <i class="mdi mdi-comment-outline prefix"></i>
                            <textarea name="message" id="message" class="materialize-textarea validate"></textarea>
                            <label for="message">Product Request...</label>
                            <span class="helper-text" data-error="Please fill this input" data-success="Okay"></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col s12 input-field">
                            <button type="submit" class="btn waves-effect waves-light" id="messageButton"><i class="mdi mdi-send left"></i>Send Message</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
